{"tid":682902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★公屋戶交富戶申報表要攞籌：慘過輪米","createTime":"2018-05-29T08:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T12:14:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4af05c69a54e974669fa38f5b4f1b74fe308b67","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"房委會去年通過收緊富戶政策，但維持公屋住戶每兩年需進行一次申報，交表時間直至後天（31日)便截止，近日正值交表高峰期。《香港01》接獲公屋居民投訴，指樂富橫頭磡邨物業服務辦事處，竟規定住戶需要「先取籌後交表」， 補交資料亦需重新「攞籌」；不少街坊需要在烈日當空下排隊領籌，高峰期排隊人數更達百人，很多長者更大呻辛苦。<br />\n街坊李小姐向《香港01》表示，由於籌號數目有限，有人連續排隊6日亦無法領籌，有長者須於凌晨5時前來排隊，才可取得籌號，她更要向公司告假3日才能交表。她坦言：「有婆婆連廁所都唔敢去&hellip;&hellip;交份表格啫！我覺得慘過輪米！」<br />\n最令李小組更感不滿的，是她曾致電房屋署投訴，但房署職員竟指其實遞交申報表根本不需要取籌，但卻稱不清楚每個外判物管辦事處的做法，對房署表示不滿；致電屋邨辦事處卻被掛線。「感到投訴無門。」<br />\n《香港01》記者已向房屋署查詢，但暫未獲回覆。橫頭磡邨物業服務辦事處職員則以正在派籌很忙為由，暫時不能回應記者電話查詢便掛線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1490931/org/9706c24e056e181e1d0dfe5326906b3b.jpg/8kDKwb5BXGaSEm2tqOIvUgUZfZ48Hjz79jRMfvY0TH4?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1490931%2Forg%2F9706c24e056e181e1d0dfe5326906b3b.jpg%2F8kDKwb5BXGaSEm2tqOIvUgUZfZ48Hjz79jRMfvY0TH4%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=6025ec6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/193422/%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4-%E5%AE%98%E5%83%9A%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91-%E6%A9%AB%E9%A0%AD%E7%A3%A1%E9%82%A8%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%A4%E5%AF%8C%E6%88%B6%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E8%A1%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%94%9E%E7%B1%8C-%E6%85%98%E9%81%8E%E8%BC%AA%E7%B1%B3#media_id=1490931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F193422%2F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2583%259A%25E6%2593%25BE%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A3%25A1%25E9%2582%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25AF%258C%25E6%2588%25B6%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%259E%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E7%25B1%25B3%23media_id%3D1490931&d=9Dv2KEQJ5IsBy%2B2prVFR%2FUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2d8b036b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/193422/%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4-%E5%AE%98%E5%83%9A%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91-%E6%A9%AB%E9%A0%AD%E7%A3%A1%E9%82%A8%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%A4%E5%AF%8C%E6%88%B6%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E8%A1%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%94%9E%E7%B1%8C-%E6%85%98%E9%81%8E%E8%BC%AA%E7%B1%B3#media_id=1490931</a>"},{"pid":"8efc20d29f557724a16f288cbff27f926000fc97","tid":682902,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a18f203b20cd6fbe6af5956f49476e3f398f8c","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>投訴人：交表情況混亂</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小姐向記者表示，樂富橫頭磡邨物業服務辦事處規定，不論交申報表及補交資料，必須先取籌才可，每個公屋家庭亦要與主任會面。不過，辦事處只有3名主任，早前更有一位主任因病告假，令交表情況非常混亂。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，派籌分兩個時段，分別為早上8時45分及下午1時45分。不過，即使她上午11時已到場，下午的籌號亦已派光，「全部公公婆婆凌晨5、6點就過來排，但早上得40個籌，即使早上7、8點到場的公公婆婆，又係白等！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有人要排足6日才可交表</strong><br />\n<br />\n李小姐又指，辦事處每日的派籌數目均不同，街坊難以準備，只能空等。「辦事處每日的派籌數目都唔同，聽街坊講，有時派60個，有時派100個，街坊根來無所適從！」她稱，有街坊需要排6天才可成功交表。<br />\n為了交表，李小姐早前向公司告假一天，怎料要臨時再請假兩日才獲到籌號，「向公司臨時請假，洗盡人情牌，隨時工都無、無埋入息，仲可以點報？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/193422/%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4-%E5%AE%98%E5%83%9A%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91-%E6%A9%AB%E9%A0%AD%E7%A3%A1%E9%82%A8%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%A4%E5%AF%8C%E6%88%B6%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E8%A1%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%94%9E%E7%B1%8C-%E6%85%98%E9%81%8E%E8%BC%AA%E7%B1%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F193422%2F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2583%259A%25E6%2593%25BE%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A3%25A1%25E9%2582%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25AF%258C%25E6%2588%25B6%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%259E%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E7%25B1%25B3&d=9Dv2KEQJ5IsBy%2B2prVFR%2FUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0d05e67a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/193422/%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4-%E5%AE%98%E5%83%9A%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91-%E6%A9%AB%E9%A0%AD%E7%A3%A1%E9%82%A8%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%A4%E5%AF%8C%E6%88%B6%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E8%A1%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%94%9E%E7%B1%8C-%E6%85%98%E9%81%8E%E8%BC%AA%E7%B1%B3</a>"},{"pid":"43f78738317b6d3f2e98568f96b103393fcb564f","tid":682902,"uid":167330,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"點解2018仲要親自交堆爛紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔可以網上分流班後生"},{"pid":"56cb622657efc7af517308fabe78c189266208ec","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1490106/org/d0d80d9ac91f6596874173d4806719cc.jpg/fqYz6CpRtVRMlY2oS4ysl3zloLHMxQqKIvTYviL02L4?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1490106%2Forg%2Fd0d80d9ac91f6596874173d4806719cc.jpg%2FfqYz6CpRtVRMlY2oS4ysl3zloLHMxQqKIvTYviL02L4%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=1279fcf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9c96953a3ce3234e5d486185b6f7378d3ab7cee","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"43f78738317b6d3f2e98568f96b103393fcb564f","tid":682902,"uid":167330,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"點解2018仲要親自交堆爛紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔可以網上分流班後生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HK No IT</span>"},{"pid":"e6996fdca542090f10b4d26f9bcee01b11ab226c","tid":682902,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"去到2018仲要交hardcopy，先進城市"},{"pid":"119de792220e95f657dc54a8fecc791960f6a5a2","tid":682902,"uid":42367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"又撚狗民"},{"pid":"e2f469c66adddd15183fa3a9c4b1212558b6843b","tid":682902,"uid":25971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"咪撚交囉 最多咪俾房署趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b2fd1899c78d5ced8a1107ec5bfcd1769fc4f1","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6996fdca542090f10b4d26f9bcee01b11ab226c","tid":682902,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"去到2018仲要交hardcopy，先進城市"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"★香港IT有幾落後---申請居屋40年不變 要遞交紙本表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/665681/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/665681/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"07fd95adc8c5cc1dea244245b7bee33ce46f0dcb","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1b2fd1899c78d5ced8a1107ec5bfcd1769fc4f1","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6996fdca542090f10b4d26f9bcee01b11ab226c","tid":682902,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"去到2018仲要交hardcopy，先進城市"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"★香港IT有幾落後---申請居屋40年不變 要遞交紙本表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/665681/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/665681/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:48:43.000Z","msg":"本年度房委會居屋項目3月29日起接受申請，相信有不少市民已完成交表。對於一眾要大費周章親身到樂富或是郵寄交表的申請者而言，或許會有一個疑問：為何上期房協資助房屋容許以網上遞交申請，可是作為全港最大業主的房委會，偏偏一定要交紙本表格這麼麻煩？<br />\n<br />\n其實政府20年前推動公共服務電子化，到今日一直把「智慧城市」擺在嘴邊，但成效如何公眾「有目共睹」。<span style=\"color: red;\">申請居屋要遞交紙本表格的方式，已經是「40年不變」</span>，到現時還是要大量申請者親身拿到辦事處交紙本表格。有立法會議員指出，房委會一直以「技術理由」推搪電子化，到現時還是沒有更新系統，認為在如今的互聯網年代，還要大批市民擠到一個地方交表，完全不合理。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>需親身交表　申請者「排到出馬路」</strong><br />\n<br />\n現行房委會遞交居屋申請方法，已經維持多年。政府自70年代推出居者有其屋計劃，1978年正式推出發售，申請者也是需要親身或郵遞交表。<br />\n<br />\n因應資訊科技的發展，政府在90年代末就開始推動公共服務電子化，加強多項政府服務，例如建立政府一站通、網上申請系統等，因此現時一些較簡單的服務例如報稅交稅、申請部分政府職位、預約康文署場地等都可在網上進行。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，房委會內部當時也研究過將居屋申請轉移到網上，便利每期數以萬計的申請者。可是後來政府在2002年宣布停建居屋，計劃也就不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n結果，在2014年底政府重推居屋後，房委會還是採取舊有的派表交表方式，綠表申請人可以交到各區屋邨辦事處，但白表人士只能交到樂富的房委會客務中心。到2015年1月12日截止交表當日，由於交表的人實在太多，人龍排到出中心外，伸延至樂富巴士總站甚至佔領部分馬路，引起不少市民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>麻煩又易出錯　排頭位申請者「慘變」二千多位</strong><br />\n<br />\n時至今日，房委會居屋申請者還是不能通過網上申請，只能在網上下載申請表，列印填好並遞交。此種做法既浪費紙張，對申請者也構成不便，市民至少也要找個信封入好文件寄出，要是不想冒寄失風險就要專程走到樂富房委會客戶服務中心交表。更麻煩的是申請費用不能交現金，只能交劃線支票或本票，對一些平日沒有用支票習慣的市民而言，既不方便，也增加出錯風險。<br />\n<br />\n房委會收到表格後，會外判聘請人手輸入資料，這既增加成本，也白白提高出錯機會。例如在2015年居屋申請之中，就有綠表申請者的資料被入錯，原本根據攪珠結果可排第1，卻變成第2,000多位，揀樓無望。而申請人本屬「家有長者優先選樓家庭」揀樓類別，卻被錯誤歸入為「中轉屋清拆計劃影響家庭」。房署最後要重新覆檢所有申請。"},{"pid":"56714986a38527704f5b3e2306e94c8843425823","tid":682902,"uid":39381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"讓返間屋出黎咪唔洗排囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d80b0a5999ad0440c739eefa560b8a781ec6c4","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56714986a38527704f5b3e2306e94c8843425823","tid":682902,"uid":39381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"讓返間屋出黎咪唔洗排囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1048b50573e7977b0dd468711fd6b2404ed74094","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>投訴人：交表情況混亂</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小姐向記者表示，樂富橫頭磡邨物業服務辦事處規定，不論交申報表及補交資料，必須先取籌才可，<span style=\"color: red;\">每個公屋家庭亦要與主任會面</span>。不過，辦事處只有3名主任，早前更有一位主任因病告假，令交表情況非常混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申請老綜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f753809eba9bc6970e9405419d0c297fb50e6918","tid":682902,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56714986a38527704f5b3e2306e94c8843425823","tid":682902,"uid":39381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"讓返間屋出黎咪唔洗排囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"咁老老實實，佢請隊IT整個system，點都化算過每區請堆外判搞仲要排晒隊掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9df7402c82a70071f4a9382a3d4ab1c38df3c5","tid":682902,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f753809eba9bc6970e9405419d0c297fb50e6918","tid":682902,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56714986a38527704f5b3e2306e94c8843425823","tid":682902,"uid":39381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"讓返間屋出黎咪唔洗排囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"咁老老實實，佢請隊IT整個system，點都化算過每區請堆外判搞仲要排晒隊掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為要保持<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HK No IT</span>型像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762d49696722151687c2711230e511e055dcfb59","tid":682902,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">很多長者更大呻辛苦</span><br />\n廢老唔係好捱得咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續支持建